# A3: a newer foreign save exists AND the local save is unpushed progress (LOCAL=unpushed —
# matches no server revision): prompt, never silently overwrite. Declining launches as-is.
desc fetch hook: LOCAL=unpushed + newer foreign save -> prompt; decline launches with local save
invoke prehook
config paired
romarg Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Zelda.gba
sdfile+ Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Zelda.gba
engine 0|202\t2026-07-02 08:00\tFlip\t33KB\n101\t2026-07-01 10:00\tBrick\t32KB\nLOCAL=unpushed
pick 2|
expect_exit 0
expect_trace LIST[Newer save from Flip — restore?]
expect_trace_absent ENGINE --restore-save
expect_log newest=foreign action=prompted
